description.p:
Following dosing, terminal blood samples were collected from each animal via cardiac puncture, and brains were excised, at each of the following time points:
Intravenous groups: 7, 15 and 30 minutes, 1, 2, 4, 8, 12 and 24 hours;
Intraperitoneal groups: 15 and 30 minutes, 1, 2, 4, 8, 12 and 24 hours.
